[SPEAKER_02] sve je dobro,

986
01:22:26,739 --> 01:22:29,399
[SPEAKER_02] davili ljekove za spavanje,

987
01:22:29,399 --> 01:22:30,319
[SPEAKER_02] ništa od toga.

988
01:22:30,319 --> 01:22:32,020
[SPEAKER_02] I evo, došao sam tu,

989
01:22:32,020 --> 01:22:32,600
[SPEAKER_02] dobro.

990
01:22:32,600 --> 01:22:36,260
[SPEAKER_02] Jesi to ispovjedio?

991
01:22:36,260 --> 01:22:36,859
[SPEAKER_02] Nisam.

992
01:22:36,859 --> 01:22:38,640
[SPEAKER_02] Ok, ajmo to ispovjedite.

993
01:22:38,640 --> 01:22:42,180
[SPEAKER_02] Prođe ispovjed,

994
01:22:42,180 --> 01:22:46,319
[SPEAKER_02] pokoru treba izmoliti,

995
01:22:46,319 --> 01:22:47,479
[SPEAKER_02] nećemo se igrati,

996
01:22:47,520 --> 01:22:48,800
[SPEAKER_02] dajmo mi pokoru zajedno,

997
01:22:48,800 --> 01:22:50,180
[SPEAKER_02] izmoli da ja budem siguran

998
01:22:50,180 --> 01:22:51,640
[SPEAKER_02] da ti to izmoliti.

999
01:22:51,640 --> 01:22:54,920
[SPEAKER_02] I drž ne daj,

1000
01:22:54,920 --> 01:22:56,560
[SPEAKER_02] ne može izmoliti,

1001
01:22:56,560 --> 01:22:57,680
[SPEAKER_02] otvara usta,

1002
01:22:57,680 --> 01:22:58,579
[SPEAKER_02] stišće usta.

1003
01:22:58,579 --> 01:23:00,920
[SPEAKER_02] Mi smo tu malu pokoricu,

1004
01:23:00,920 --> 01:23:03,100
[SPEAKER_02] koja traje minutu,

1005
01:23:03,100 --> 01:23:05,119
[SPEAKER_02] molili 15 minuta.

1006
01:23:05,119 --> 01:23:06,460
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, hvala Bogu,

1007
01:23:06,460 --> 01:23:07,140
[SPEAKER_02] završio je.

1008
01:23:07,140 --> 01:23:09,359
[SPEAKER_02] Izmolio vam to.

1009
01:23:09,359 --> 01:23:12,100
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sad, mislim se,

1010
01:23:12,100 --> 01:23:13,720
[SPEAKER_02] šta ćemo sad dalje,

1011
01:23:13,720 --> 01:23:15,600
[SPEAKER_02] kakši šat,

1012
01:23:15,600 --> 01:23:16,279
[SPEAKER_02] pa bolje,

1013
01:23:16,279 --> 01:23:17,220
[SPEAKER_02] bolje se osjećam.

1014
01:23:17,520 --> 01:23:21,939
[SPEAKER_02] ispričao mi je,

1015
01:23:21,939 --> 01:23:22,319
[SPEAKER_02] da,

1016
01:23:22,319 --> 01:23:24,000
[SPEAKER_02] u toj svom stanju,

1017
01:23:24,000 --> 01:23:25,659
[SPEAKER_02] nije opće mogao biti na misu.

1018
01:23:25,659 --> 01:23:27,640
[SPEAKER_02] Čim bude uđe u crkvu,

1019
01:23:27,640 --> 01:23:28,979
[SPEAKER_02] bude malo,

1020
01:23:28,979 --> 01:23:30,140
[SPEAKER_02] toliko se uznemiri,

1021
01:23:30,140 --> 01:23:31,880
[SPEAKER_02] u njemu to da mora van,

1022
01:23:31,880 --> 01:23:32,520
[SPEAKER_02] da se smiri.

1023
01:23:32,520 --> 01:23:34,760
[SPEAKER_02] Ja mu kažem,

1024
01:23:34,760 --> 01:23:35,380
[SPEAKER_02] onda dobro,

1025
01:23:35,380 --> 01:23:36,920
[SPEAKER_02] sad ćeš tići sa mnom na misu,

1026
01:23:37,659 --> 01:23:38,640
[SPEAKER_02] ministrirat ćeš mi,

1027
01:23:38,640 --> 01:23:40,420
[SPEAKER_02] i onda ćemo vidjet dalje.

1028
01:23:42,340 --> 01:23:43,479
[SPEAKER_02] bude dano sa mnom,

1029
01:23:43,479 --> 01:23:44,399
[SPEAKER_02] ministrirat,

1030
01:23:44,399 --> 01:23:45,300
[SPEAKER_02] sav sretan,

1031
01:23:45,300 --> 01:23:45,840
[SPEAKER_02] cvjeta,

1032
01:23:45,840 --> 01:23:47,420
[SPEAKER_02] završi,

1033
01:23:47,420 --> 01:23:48,159
[SPEAKER_02] još ostane,

1034
01:23:48,159 --> 01:23:49,140
[SPEAKER_02] umoliti zajedno,

1035
01:23:49,140 --> 01:23:49,819
[SPEAKER_02] malo budemo,

1036
01:23:49,819 --> 01:23:51,520
[SPEAKER_02] klanjanje kratko,

1037
01:23:51,520 --> 01:23:53,000
[SPEAKER_02] izađemo van,

1038
01:23:53,000 --> 01:23:54,380
[SPEAKER_02] ja mu dan svoj broj,

1039
01:23:54,380 --> 01:23:54,619
[SPEAKER_02] evo,

1040
01:23:54,619 --> 01:23:55,479
[SPEAKER_02] tu ti je moj broj,

1041
01:23:56,199 --> 01:23:58,520
[SPEAKER_02] ako se bude to ponavljalo,

1042
01:23:58,520 --> 01:23:59,439
[SPEAKER_02] nazovimo,

1043
01:23:59,439 --> 01:24:00,760
[SPEAKER_02] ja ću te onda posla dalje,

1044
01:24:00,760 --> 01:24:02,100
[SPEAKER_02] gdje šta treba,

1045
01:24:02,100 --> 01:24:03,720
[SPEAKER_02] međutim,

1046
01:24:03,720 --> 01:24:05,079
[SPEAKER_02] rješeno.

1047
01:24:05,079 --> 01:24:06,659
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

1048
01:24:06,659 --> 01:24:08,640
[SPEAKER_02] snaga jedne ispovjedi,

1049
01:24:08,640 --> 01:24:10,880
[SPEAKER_02] ovo je bio jednostavan slučaj,

1050
01:24:10,880 --> 01:24:12,119
[SPEAKER_02] da tako kažem,

1051
01:24:12,119 --> 01:24:15,220
[SPEAKER_02] gdje on to praktički nakon par dana odmah rješio,

1052
01:24:15,220 --> 01:24:16,399
[SPEAKER_02] i to je bio jednokratno,

1053
01:24:16,399 --> 01:24:20,000
[SPEAKER_02] dakle nije bilo neke duge povijesti,

1054
01:24:20,000 --> 01:24:20,939
[SPEAKER_02] ponavljanja,

1055
01:24:20,939 --> 01:24:22,479
[SPEAKER_02] niti je bila neka pozadina,

1056
01:24:22,479 --> 01:24:26,460
[SPEAKER_02] u smislu neke traume,

1057
01:24:26,460 --> 01:24:27,899
[SPEAKER_02] nekog života,

1058
01:24:27,899 --> 01:24:29,380
[SPEAKER_02] u navici nekoj,

1059
01:24:29,380 --> 01:24:31,279
[SPEAKER_02] dakle bilo je sve vrlo čisto,

1060
01:24:31,279 --> 01:24:33,760
[SPEAKER_02] pa se je i vrlo jednostavno rješilo.

1061
01:24:33,760 --> 01:24:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] Imam pitanje,

1062
01:24:35,920 --> 01:24:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo govorili o toj nekakvim napadima,

1063
01:24:41,340 --> 01:24:42,979
[SPEAKER_00] izvanrednim i duhovnom boju,

1064
01:24:42,979 --> 01:24:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] spomenuli ste na početku da često,

1065
01:24:45,920 --> 01:24:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] ko što je i ona išao na vijestit,

1066
01:24:48,119 --> 01:24:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] i da tu često dođe nekakva napast,

1067
01:24:51,100 --> 01:24:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] ili bi se mi koji se trudimo živjeti vjeru

1068
01:24:53,680 --> 01:24:55,560
[SPEAKER_00] i služimo u zajednicama ili negdje,

1069
01:24:55,560 --> 01:24:59,439
[SPEAKER_00] ili bi se trebali bojati odmazde?

1070
01:24:59,439 --> 01:25:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] Često se molete molitve zaštite i to je ok,

1071
01:25:02,859 --> 01:25:05,140
[SPEAKER_00] ali ili bi se trebali bojati odmazde?

1072
01:25:05,140 --> 01:25:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, često to vjerojatno zna ljude,

1073
01:25:07,319 --> 01:25:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] ko ćete da uopće uđu,

1074
01:25:08,819 --> 01:25:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] ono kalkuliraju.

1075
01:25:10,239 --> 01:25:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna stvar je da nisi pozva na to.

1076
01:25:12,079 --> 01:25:16,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, ali zajednica ide napraviti nekakav veliki projekt,

1077
01:25:16,859 --> 01:25:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] ti si dio zajednice evangelizacijski,

1078
01:25:18,460 --> 01:25:19,939
[SPEAKER_00] i počneš kalkulirati,

1079
01:25:19,939 --> 01:25:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] pa ok, ja ne znam, pa kajak ovo,

1080
01:25:22,220 --> 01:25:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa kajak meni sjedne na ovo,

1081
01:25:23,500 --> 01:25:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] pa kajak mi sjedne na familiju.

1082
01:25:24,760 --> 01:25:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] Iskustvo jednog i drugog mi je tu važno.

1083
01:25:27,640 --> 01:25:29,939
[SPEAKER_00] Vas ko autoriteta, definitivno ko svećenika,

1084
01:25:29,939 --> 01:25:33,319
[SPEAKER_00] a iskustvo zajednice i...

1085
01:25:33,319 --> 01:25:33,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ti prvi.

1086
01:25:33,899 --> 01:25:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš ti prvi.

1087
01:25:34,579 --> 01:25:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] Da ja prvi.

1088
01:25:35,199 --> 01:25:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ti prvi.

1089
01:25:35,739 --> 01:25:36,479
[SPEAKER_02] Može.

1090
01:25:36,479 --> 01:25:39,619
[SPEAKER_02] Pa, znači ne treba se bojati.

1091
01:25:39,619 --> 01:25:41,500
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo, ne treba se bojati.

1092
01:25:41,500 --> 01:25:43,399
[SPEAKER_02] Strah je...

1093
01:25:43,399 --> 01:25:45,439
[SPEAKER_02] Strah, znači nije strah Božji.

1094
01:25:45,439 --> 01:25:46,140
[SPEAKER_02] To su dva različite stvari.

1095
01:25:46,140 --> 01:25:46,819
[SPEAKER_02] Treba dolazi od Boga.

1096
01:25:46,819 --> 01:25:47,800
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je.

1097
01:25:47,800 --> 01:25:50,699
[SPEAKER_02] Strah je taktika zloga.

1098
01:25:50,699 --> 01:25:52,619
[SPEAKER_02] Svjeti Ivan kaže,

1099
01:25:52,619 --> 01:25:54,220
[SPEAKER_02] u pravoj ljubavi nema straha.

1100
01:25:54,220 --> 01:25:56,859
[SPEAKER_02] Pravi strah koji dolazi od Boga

1101
01:25:56,859 --> 01:25:59,180
[SPEAKER_02] je straho poštovanje, mudrost.

1102
01:25:59,180 --> 01:26:00,960
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, to je ono što nama treba.

1103
01:26:01,760 --> 01:26:04,680
[SPEAKER_02] A mudrost pretpostavlja svijest

1104
01:26:04,680 --> 01:26:06,600
[SPEAKER_02] i znanje o tome.

1105
01:26:06,600 --> 01:26:09,340
[SPEAKER_02] Kad ja znam šta se događa u duhovnom svijetu,

1106
01:26:09,340 --> 01:26:11,640
[SPEAKER_02] ja sve lijepo napravim

1107
01:26:11,640 --> 01:26:12,659
[SPEAKER_02] i ne da se šta bojati.

1108
01:26:12,659 --> 01:26:15,119
[SPEAKER_02] To je kao kad ideš autom na put.

1109
01:26:15,119 --> 01:26:16,739
[SPEAKER_02] Šta trebaš napraviti?

1110
01:26:16,739 --> 01:26:17,600
[SPEAKER_02] Trebaš pogledati.

1111
01:26:17,600 --> 01:26:18,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ako ideš na duži put,

1112
01:26:18,420 --> 01:26:19,220
[SPEAKER_02] pogledaš ulje,

1113
01:26:19,220 --> 01:26:20,119
[SPEAKER_02] pogledaš vodu,

1114
01:26:20,119 --> 01:26:20,880
[SPEAKER_02] pogledaš gume,

1115
01:26:20,880 --> 01:26:22,220
[SPEAKER_02] uđeš unutra,

1116
01:26:22,220 --> 01:26:23,100
[SPEAKER_02] zavežeš se

1117
01:26:23,100 --> 01:26:24,579
[SPEAKER_02] i voziš po pravilima.

1118
01:26:24,579 --> 01:26:26,100
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je i u ovome.

1119
01:26:26,100 --> 01:26:27,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ako radiš po pravilima,

1120
01:26:27,420 --> 01:26:29,439
[SPEAKER_02] ako si ponizan,

1121
01:26:29,439 --> 01:26:31,079
[SPEAKER_02] ako si u milosti,

1122
01:26:31,640 --> 01:26:33,520
[SPEAKER_02] i ako imaš podršku zajednice,

1123
01:26:33,520 --> 01:26:37,260
[SPEAKER_02] ako si napravio sve što treba napraviti,

1124
01:26:37,260 --> 01:26:38,819
[SPEAKER_02] sluga sam beskorisan

1125
01:26:38,819 --> 01:26:39,500
[SPEAKER_02] i to je to.

1126
01:26:39,500 --> 01:26:41,460
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, to je ovako ukratko.

1127
01:26:41,460 --> 01:26:42,279
[SPEAKER_02] Dosta praktično.

1128
01:26:42,279 --> 01:26:42,720
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

1129
01:26:42,720 --> 01:26:44,600
[SPEAKER_01] Baš upravo to.

1130
01:26:44,600 --> 01:26:45,939
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, mi smo imali,

1131
01:26:45,939 --> 01:26:46,560
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

1132
01:26:46,560 --> 01:26:48,680
[SPEAKER_01] radjeći kroz dogini izgodina

1133
01:26:48,680 --> 01:26:49,819
[SPEAKER_01] sa zajednicama

1134
01:26:49,819 --> 01:26:51,100
[SPEAKER_01] i takvim ražnim projektima,

1135
01:26:51,100 --> 01:26:52,560
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo svakakvih iskustava,

1136
01:26:52,560 --> 01:26:54,239
[SPEAKER_01] ali je zanimljivo da Bog,

1137
01:26:54,939 --> 01:26:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] baš ako nešto i dopusti,

1138
01:26:56,180 --> 01:26:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] recimo nekako gnjetavanje,

1139
01:26:58,500 --> 01:27:00,760
[SPEAKER_01] da ti pukne guma na automobilu ili,

1140
01:27:00,760 --> 01:27:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] bilo je takvih situacija,

1141
01:27:03,119 --> 01:27:06,899
[SPEAKER_01] ali zanimljivo je da nikad se nije dogodilo ništa više nego...

1142
01:27:06,899 --> 01:27:07,680
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je okej.

1143
01:27:07,680 --> 01:27:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] Puknut guma,

1144
01:27:08,359 --> 01:27:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek je pitanje za ono neke stvari

1145
01:27:10,380 --> 01:27:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] koje su nama bitne svete.

1146
01:27:12,079 --> 01:27:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ako moja žena i djete

1147
01:27:14,079 --> 01:27:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] koji su doma,

1148
01:27:14,760 --> 01:27:16,600
[SPEAKER_00] sad na njih sjedne i udari?

1149
01:27:16,600 --> 01:27:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pa gle,

1150
01:27:17,340 --> 01:27:17,840
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1151
01:27:17,840 --> 01:27:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] iskustvo je da mogu doći male kušnje.

1152
01:27:20,260 --> 01:27:21,340
[SPEAKER_01] A kad kažem male kušnje,

1153
01:27:21,340 --> 01:27:23,600
[SPEAKER_01] one koje nas neće opteretiti,

1154
01:27:23,600 --> 01:27:24,560
[SPEAKER_01] nego će nas povući,

1155
01:27:24,560 --> 01:27:26,239
[SPEAKER_01] da idemo u molitvu.

1156
01:27:26,239 --> 01:27:26,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, je kao...

1157
01:27:26,760 --> 01:27:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] To je dobro, to mi je dobro.

1158
01:27:27,659 --> 01:27:28,119
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1159
01:27:28,119 --> 01:27:29,319
[SPEAKER_01] To mi je okej.

1160
01:27:29,319 --> 01:27:32,260
[SPEAKER_01] Problemi nastaju ako ne poštivam autoritet.

1161
01:27:33,220 --> 01:27:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] problemi mogu nastati.

1162
01:27:34,199 --> 01:27:35,979
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja sam sada Super Mario,

1163
01:27:35,979 --> 01:27:38,420
[SPEAKER_01] pa idem se boriti sa...

1164
01:27:38,420 --> 01:27:40,140
[SPEAKER_01] Idem ja ovo i ovo rješavati.

1165
01:27:40,140 --> 01:27:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] E, onda to može biti tekako.

1166
01:27:42,119 --> 01:27:43,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad čovjek ide u zajednje,

1167
01:27:43,479 --> 01:27:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] što kad ide u poslušnosti autoritetu,

1168
01:27:45,880 --> 01:27:46,520
[SPEAKER_01] kojemu je dan,

1169
01:27:46,520 --> 01:27:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] i kad ta ekipa koja to radi,

1170
01:27:49,239 --> 01:27:50,859
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći već u određenoj mjeri,

1171
01:27:50,859 --> 01:27:51,560
[SPEAKER_01] putem,

1172
01:27:51,560 --> 01:27:51,899
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1173
01:27:51,899 --> 01:27:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] Bog nas uvijek vodi,

1174
01:27:53,300 --> 01:27:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] evo, nikad nas ne dovede do situacije,

1175
01:27:55,420 --> 01:27:56,560
[SPEAKER_01] e, sad, skoči s hrame.

1176
01:27:56,560 --> 01:27:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nego ti ideš putem, hodaš,

1177
01:27:58,579 --> 01:28:00,399
[SPEAKER_01] hodaš sljedeći njega,

1178
01:28:00,479 --> 01:28:01,520
[SPEAKER_01] evangelizirajući,

1179
01:28:01,520 --> 01:28:03,319
[SPEAKER_01] radeći jedan život zajednic,

1180
01:28:03,319 --> 01:28:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] jedan život obitelji.

1181
01:28:04,380 --> 01:28:07,659
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, ako se dogodi da se nađe nekakva zamka,

1182
01:28:07,659 --> 01:28:09,359
[SPEAKER_01] kako kaže i sveto pismo,

1183
01:28:09,359 --> 01:28:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] on nas čuva o te zamke.

1184
01:28:10,880 --> 01:28:12,779
[SPEAKER_01] On nas čuva da se ne spotaknemo putem.

1185
01:28:12,779 --> 01:28:14,640
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on je taj koji je naš branitelj.

1186
01:28:14,640 --> 01:28:15,880
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

1187
01:28:15,880 --> 01:28:18,020
[SPEAKER_01] apsolutno se ne treba bojati,

1188
01:28:18,020 --> 01:28:19,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali treba biti svjesnim tih stvari.

1189
01:28:19,659 --> 01:28:21,439
[SPEAKER_01] I zato jesu određene molitve.

1190
01:28:21,439 --> 01:28:23,279
[SPEAKER_01] Crkva je prepoznavala kroz povijest

1191
01:28:23,279 --> 01:28:25,439
[SPEAKER_01] da određene molitve su dobro ih ima.

1192
01:28:25,439 --> 01:28:27,819
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je uvijek to pokajanje, opraštanje

1193
01:28:27,819 --> 01:28:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] ili kad završiš služenje,

1194
01:28:29,420 --> 01:28:30,439
[SPEAKER_01] doći k Bogu.

1195
01:28:30,439 --> 01:28:32,560
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nije najvažnije ono što si ti služio,

1196
01:28:32,560 --> 01:28:34,399
[SPEAKER_01] nego to da nakon dođeš k njemu.

1197
01:28:34,399 --> 01:28:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] U intimiji srca.

1198
01:28:35,279 --> 01:28:37,439
[SPEAKER_01] Da njega počastiš svojom ljubavlji,

1199
01:28:37,439 --> 01:28:38,520
[SPEAKER_01] svojom prisutnosti.

1200
01:28:38,520 --> 01:28:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] I samo te to već čuva.

1201
01:28:39,960 --> 01:28:43,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako ja idem tamo i trčim da bi neke stvari radio,

1202
01:28:43,180 --> 01:28:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] da bi bio super...

1203
01:28:44,380 --> 01:28:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] Iskustvo nas poučava

1204
01:28:50,039 --> 01:28:52,939
[SPEAKER_01] da je dobro uvijek se utjecati

1205
01:28:52,939 --> 01:28:54,600
[SPEAKER_01] onim molitvama koje crkva preporučila.

1206
01:28:54,600 --> 01:28:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] Imate molitvom Svetom Mihajlu,

1207
01:28:55,960 --> 01:28:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] Svetim anđelima, čuvarima.

1208
01:28:57,539 --> 01:28:59,939
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su nevjerojatno snažna pomoć

1209
01:28:59,939 --> 01:29:03,180
[SPEAKER_01] u našem obiteljskom životu.

1210
01:29:03,180 --> 01:29:06,340
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, radeći na mnoge ljude

1211
01:29:06,340 --> 01:29:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] koji su imali tolike pomoće od anđela, čuvara.

1212
01:29:08,539 --> 01:29:09,619
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, jedni moji prijatelj,

1213
01:29:09,619 --> 01:29:10,439
[SPEAKER_01] jedan brašni par,

1214
01:29:10,439 --> 01:29:13,520
[SPEAKER_01] je imao jednu situaciju

1215
01:29:13,520 --> 01:29:14,939
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su imali jednu kušnju.

1216
01:29:14,939 --> 01:29:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] Malo je tu bilo pitanje

1217
01:29:17,180 --> 01:29:19,159
[SPEAKER_01] i ega i svega

1218
01:29:19,159 --> 01:29:21,020
[SPEAKER_01] i dogodila se jedna snažna svađa

1219
01:29:21,020 --> 01:29:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] između njih dvoje.

1220
01:29:21,920 --> 01:29:24,180
[SPEAKER_01] I u tom trenutku je to izgledalo

1221
01:29:24,180 --> 01:29:25,859
[SPEAKER_01] jako, jako, jako loše.

1222
01:29:25,859 --> 01:29:26,979
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

1223
01:29:26,979 --> 01:29:29,319
[SPEAKER_01] nevjerojatno kako se Bog proslavi,

1224
01:29:29,319 --> 01:29:30,600
[SPEAKER_01] bili su Bogu vjerni,

1225
01:29:30,600 --> 01:29:33,239
[SPEAKER_01] njima u tom trenutku

1226
01:29:33,239 --> 01:29:34,060
[SPEAKER_01] zazvani telefon.

1227
01:29:34,060 --> 01:29:35,939
[SPEAKER_01] U najvećem trenutku svađe,

1228
01:29:35,939 --> 01:29:37,399
[SPEAKER_01] njima zoni telefon

1229
01:29:37,399 --> 01:29:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] i zove ih jedna osoba

1230
01:29:39,760 --> 01:29:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] koja inače nikad ne kontaktira,

1231
01:29:42,420 --> 01:29:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] a ta osoba kao vidi anđele.

1232
01:29:44,279 --> 01:29:47,680
[SPEAKER_01] E sad, često kod tog gledanja

1233
01:29:47,680 --> 01:29:49,859
[SPEAKER_01] anđela ima jako puno svega

1234
01:29:49,859 --> 01:29:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] tih istočnjačkih stvari

1235
01:29:51,340 --> 01:29:53,520
[SPEAKER_01] i to onda u biti i demoni su anđeli.

1236
01:29:53,720 --> 01:29:54,979
[SPEAKER_01] A ovdje govorimo anđelima,

1237
01:29:54,979 --> 01:29:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] čuvarima konkretnim.

1238
01:29:56,420 --> 01:29:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] I što se dogodi?

1239
01:29:57,460 --> 01:29:59,720
[SPEAKER_01] U tom trenutku ta osoba se javi

1240
01:29:59,720 --> 01:30:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] na telefonu u čudu što se događa,

1241
01:30:01,340 --> 01:30:01,979
[SPEAKER_01] zašto vas zove?

1242
01:30:01,979 --> 01:30:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] U trenutku najgore je svađa.

1243
01:30:03,039 --> 01:30:04,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, nikad prije, nikad poslije

1244
01:30:04,279 --> 01:30:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] nisim imala takvu svađu.

1245
01:30:05,260 --> 01:30:07,060
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže, ova osoba se javlja,

1246
01:30:07,060 --> 01:30:07,939
[SPEAKER_01] kaže, što se događa?

1247
01:30:07,939 --> 01:30:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] Došao je tvoj anđel, čuvar,

1248
01:30:09,239 --> 01:30:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] moliti za pomoć.

1249
01:30:10,920 --> 01:30:12,300
[SPEAKER_01] On plače i traži da molimo

1250
01:30:12,300 --> 01:30:13,840
[SPEAKER_01] za tebe i tvoju ženu.

1251
01:30:13,840 --> 01:30:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto to govorim?

1252
01:30:15,180 --> 01:30:17,140
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, želim pokazati kako Bog

1253
01:30:17,140 --> 01:30:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] nam je dao takvu snažne prijatelje

1254
01:30:18,960 --> 01:30:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] i pomoć, poput anđela čuvara,

1255
01:30:21,199 --> 01:30:22,579
[SPEAKER_01] poput svetog Mihajla,

1256
01:30:22,579 --> 01:30:24,359
[SPEAKER_01] ova moletva,

1257
01:30:24,359 --> 01:30:26,600
[SPEAKER_01] gospi po tvoju obranu se utječemo.

1258
01:30:26,600 --> 01:30:28,520
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, imamo takve snažne moletve

1259
01:30:28,520 --> 01:30:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] za krv Kristovu.

1260
01:30:29,619 --> 01:30:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi smo pozvani,

1261
01:30:31,079 --> 01:30:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] kao što je u Egiptu,

1262
01:30:32,880 --> 01:30:35,060
[SPEAKER_01] Mojsi je dao da se zaštite

1263
01:30:35,060 --> 01:30:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] njihove kuće, njihove domovi.

1264
01:30:37,420 --> 01:30:39,500
[SPEAKER_01] Tako mi imamo snagu da možemo

1265
01:30:39,500 --> 01:30:41,359
[SPEAKER_01] krv Kristovu zazvati na sebe,

1266
01:30:41,359 --> 01:30:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] na svoju obitelj, na svoju zajednicu.

1267
01:30:43,000 --> 01:30:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] I samim time, kad njih zaštitima se,

1268
01:30:45,239 --> 01:30:46,560
[SPEAKER_01] ne može nam niko ništa.

1269
01:30:46,560 --> 01:30:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] Bila jedna situacija,

1270
01:30:47,760 --> 01:30:49,899
[SPEAKER_01] evo baš jedan bivši sotonistima,

1271
01:30:49,899 --> 01:30:51,359
[SPEAKER_01] možete to naći na internetu,

1272
01:30:51,359 --> 01:30:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] on imao tako jednu situaciju,

1273
01:30:52,819 --> 01:30:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] dvije, evo recimo dvije.

1274
01:30:54,000 --> 01:30:55,899
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna je bila gdje on želi uništiti

1275
01:30:55,899 --> 01:30:57,560
[SPEAKER_01] jednu stariju ženu.

1276
01:30:57,560 --> 01:30:58,720
[SPEAKER_01] On je znao, znači,

1277
01:30:58,720 --> 01:30:59,880
[SPEAKER_01] oni koji nisu,

1278
01:30:59,880 --> 01:31:02,560
[SPEAKER_01] znao je takvim silama i snagama,

1279
01:31:02,560 --> 01:31:03,140
[SPEAKER_01] jer su bili,

1280
01:31:03,140 --> 01:31:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] on bi po cijelu noć boravio

1281
01:31:04,720 --> 01:31:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] sa svojim gospodarom,

1282
01:31:06,119 --> 01:31:06,779
[SPEAKER_01] sa sotonom,

1283
01:31:06,779 --> 01:31:08,819
[SPEAKER_01] za raz kod nas vjernika,

1284
01:31:08,819 --> 01:31:09,819
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ne možem jednu noć,

1285
01:31:09,819 --> 01:31:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] jedan sat,

1286
01:31:10,460 --> 01:31:12,600
[SPEAKER_01] jedan sat ne možeš probiljati

1287
01:31:12,600 --> 01:31:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] sa svojim Bogom.

1288
01:31:13,340 --> 01:31:14,479
[SPEAKER_01] I što se dogodilo?

1289
01:31:14,479 --> 01:31:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] On je trebao nju uništiti,

1290
01:31:15,920 --> 01:31:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] jer me neko da li platio nešto.

1291
01:31:17,300 --> 01:31:18,100
[SPEAKER_01] I što se događa?

1292
01:31:18,100 --> 01:31:20,220
[SPEAKER_01] On je počeo i nije mogao ništa.

1293
01:31:21,140 --> 01:31:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] On nije mogao ništa.

1294
01:31:22,960 --> 01:31:25,640
[SPEAKER_01] I on dolazi kasnije svom gospodaru,

1295
01:31:25,640 --> 01:31:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] kaže, zašto nisam mogao ništa?

1296
01:31:28,920 --> 01:31:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] A kaže, a onaj nije dao.

1297
01:31:30,880 --> 01:31:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] A kaže, ja sam prvi put shvatio

1298
01:31:32,760 --> 01:31:34,180
[SPEAKER_01] da postoji neko kojiza.

1299
01:31:34,180 --> 01:31:35,560
[SPEAKER_01] A što se u biti događalo?

1300
01:31:35,560 --> 01:31:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ta starica, ta žena,

1301
01:31:37,699 --> 01:31:40,680
[SPEAKER_01] ona je samo zazivala krv Kristovu.

1302
01:31:40,680 --> 01:31:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] Isusa, sine Bože, zaštiti mene,

1303
01:31:42,739 --> 01:31:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] zaštiti moju obitelj.

1304
01:31:43,840 --> 01:31:44,760
[SPEAKER_01] Krvi Kristov.

1305
01:31:44,760 --> 01:31:46,899
[SPEAKER_01] I najveći sotonisti nije mogao ništa.

1306
01:31:46,899 --> 01:31:48,600
[SPEAKER_01] Imate drugu situaciju.

1307
01:31:48,680 --> 01:31:51,899
[SPEAKER_01] Često, on se obratio baš vrlo snažno.

1308
01:31:51,899 --> 01:31:54,479
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je vrlo cijenjen u tim krugovima.

1309
01:31:54,479 --> 01:31:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] I on je doživio sve obraćenje

1310
01:31:56,300 --> 01:31:57,520
[SPEAKER_01] kad je došao jednoj ženi

1311
01:31:57,520 --> 01:31:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] u zlatarnu.

1312
01:31:59,659 --> 01:32:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] On je nešto htio odraditi.

1313
01:32:01,079 --> 01:32:05,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, on je radio u zlatarni kao prodavač.

1314
01:32:05,020 --> 01:32:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] I došla jedna žena

1315
01:32:06,539 --> 01:32:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dok se razgovaralo,

1316
01:32:08,380 --> 01:32:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] ona mu je stavila na ruku

1317
01:32:09,380 --> 01:32:11,220
[SPEAKER_01] posvećenu čudotvornu medaljicu.

1318
01:32:11,220 --> 01:32:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, u tom trenutku,

1319
01:32:13,220 --> 01:32:15,640
[SPEAKER_01] kaže taj bivši sotonist,

1320
01:32:15,640 --> 01:32:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] kaže, da je njega

1321
01:32:17,079 --> 01:32:19,560
[SPEAKER_01] tako prožila takva snaga,

1322
01:32:19,560 --> 01:32:20,359
[SPEAKER_01] takva vatra.

1323
01:32:20,359 --> 01:32:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] On je mogo izdržati to.

1324
01:32:21,699 --> 01:32:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] On je prvi put vidio da je ovo nešto daleko jače

1325
01:32:24,380 --> 01:32:27,520
[SPEAKER_01] nego što se on susreta u cijelom svom životu.

1326
01:32:27,520 --> 01:32:29,720
[SPEAKER_01] I tada je počelo njega zanimati što je to.

1327
01:32:29,720 --> 01:32:31,479
[SPEAKER_01] I zato nam crkva, kad vidimo,

1328
01:32:31,479 --> 01:32:33,479
[SPEAKER_01] ona nam daje tako snažno oružje.

1329
01:32:33,600 --> 01:32:35,600
[SPEAKER_01] Znači nema jačeg, kad kažem oružje,

1330
01:32:35,600 --> 01:32:36,319
[SPEAKER_01] nije to oružje,

1331
01:32:36,319 --> 01:32:37,380
[SPEAKER_01] sakramenti.

1332
01:32:37,380 --> 01:32:39,279
[SPEAKER_01] Živje sakramentalan život.

1333
01:32:39,279 --> 01:32:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] Živje to osobni život molitve,

1334
01:32:41,079 --> 01:32:42,140
[SPEAKER_01] riječi Božje.

1335
01:32:42,140 --> 01:32:43,760
[SPEAKER_01] Molitve opraštanja,

1336
01:32:43,760 --> 01:32:45,159
[SPEAKER_01] znači biti u miru jednim zrugima.

1337
01:32:45,159 --> 01:32:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ali onda tu dodamo još ove sakramentale

1338
01:32:47,800 --> 01:32:48,640
[SPEAKER_01] koje smo spominjali.

1339
01:32:49,020 --> 01:32:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] Imate, ne znam, čudotornu medaljicu.

1340
01:32:50,920 --> 01:32:53,199
[SPEAKER_01] Medaljicu posvećenu Svetom Benediktu

1341
01:32:53,199 --> 01:32:55,140
[SPEAKER_01] koje su vrlo snažne za zaštitu.

1342
01:32:55,140 --> 01:32:57,020
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo kod sakramentala,

1343
01:32:57,020 --> 01:32:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

1344
01:32:58,260 --> 01:33:00,659
[SPEAKER_01] blagoslovljena sol, ulje, voda.

1345
01:33:00,659 --> 01:33:02,180
[SPEAKER_01] Znači crkva nam to daje

1346
01:33:02,180 --> 01:33:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] da to koristimo

1347
01:33:03,460 --> 01:33:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] za zaštitu naših obitelji,

1348
01:33:05,699 --> 01:33:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] za blagoslov zdravlja

1349
01:33:07,300 --> 01:33:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] koje se može staviti u hranu,

1350
01:33:08,840 --> 01:33:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se može staviti blagosloviti kuća,

1351
01:33:10,960 --> 01:33:11,840
[SPEAKER_01] ulazi u kuću.

1352
01:33:11,840 --> 01:33:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] I onda jednostavno vidite

1353
01:33:13,699 --> 01:33:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] da ste puno jače zaštićeni.

1354
01:33:15,500 --> 01:33:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, kažem, to su primjeri...

1355
01:33:17,340 --> 01:33:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mi je bilo jedno pitanje.

1356
01:33:18,239 --> 01:33:21,359
[SPEAKER_00] Mi svi imate neki osjećaj sigurnosti

1357
01:33:21,359 --> 01:33:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslovljene medaljice.

1358
01:33:24,340 --> 01:33:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] Svi blagoslovljamo krunice

1359
01:33:25,899 --> 01:33:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] i vešamo ih u retrovizora.

1360
01:33:27,140 --> 01:33:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kaj je s tim?

1361
01:33:31,699 --> 01:33:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

1362
01:33:33,300 --> 01:33:34,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, ništa.

1363
01:33:34,600 --> 01:33:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne, mislim,

1364
01:33:36,000 --> 01:33:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] jer ta blagoslovljena krunica

1365
01:33:38,180 --> 01:33:39,100
[SPEAKER_00] sama po sebi

1366
01:33:39,100 --> 01:33:40,760
[SPEAKER_00] ima neku moć

1367
01:33:40,760 --> 01:33:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] ili bi ona...

1368
01:33:43,199 --> 01:33:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili je efekt neki drugi?

1369
01:33:44,880 --> 01:33:45,899
[SPEAKER_00] To visi o mojoj vjeri.

1370
01:33:47,079 --> 01:33:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala, ili zašto ja nosim evo ko vrata?

1371
01:33:48,960 --> 01:33:49,979
[SPEAKER_00] To ima smisla

1372
01:33:49,979 --> 01:33:51,819
[SPEAKER_02] ako smo mi u odnosu s Bogom,

1373
01:33:51,819 --> 01:33:54,699
[SPEAKER_02] ako smo mi u odnosu prijateljstvu s Gospom,

1374
01:33:54,699 --> 01:33:56,220
[SPEAKER_02] ako njegujemo taj odnos,

1375
01:33:56,220 --> 01:33:58,500
[SPEAKER_02] to onda ima smisla,

1376
01:33:58,500 --> 01:34:00,939
[SPEAKER_02] jer svaka ta stvar

1377
01:34:00,939 --> 01:34:03,500
[SPEAKER_02] nije sama po sebi jaka,

1378
01:34:03,500 --> 01:34:05,100
[SPEAKER_02] nije krunica sama po sebi jaka,

1379
01:34:05,100 --> 01:34:06,500
[SPEAKER_02] nego je jaka

1380
01:34:06,500 --> 01:34:07,760
[SPEAKER_02] zato jer ona predstavlja

1381
01:34:07,760 --> 01:34:08,979
[SPEAKER_02] vječni život,

1382
01:34:08,979 --> 01:34:10,640
[SPEAKER_02] vječne stvarnosti

1383
01:34:10,640 --> 01:34:12,720
[SPEAKER_02] koje su žive,

1384
01:34:12,720 --> 01:34:13,560
[SPEAKER_02] koje su vječne,

1385
01:34:13,560 --> 01:34:14,560
[SPEAKER_02] Gospa je vječna,

1386
01:34:14,560 --> 01:34:15,100
[SPEAKER_02] ona je živa,

1387
01:34:15,100 --> 01:34:15,939
[SPEAKER_02] ona je kraljica

1388
01:34:15,939 --> 01:34:17,239
[SPEAKER_02] neba i zemlje,

1389
01:34:17,239 --> 01:34:19,119
[SPEAKER_02] ona je ona koja satire glavu zmi,

1390
01:34:19,119 --> 01:34:19,920
[SPEAKER_02] recimo tako,

1391
01:34:19,920 --> 01:34:22,300
[SPEAKER_02] samo nju uzimajući za primjer.

1392
01:34:22,300 --> 01:34:23,640
[SPEAKER_02] To onda ima smisla,

1393
01:34:23,640 --> 01:34:26,020
[SPEAKER_02] jer ona predstavlja tu stvarnost

1394
01:34:26,020 --> 01:34:27,859
[SPEAKER_02] koja je nama dana na raspolaganje.

1395
01:34:27,859 --> 01:34:29,859
[SPEAKER_02] Ona je majka koja se za nas brine.

1396
01:34:30,279 --> 01:34:31,800
[SPEAKER_02] I ako se mi stavimo po njenu zaštitu,

1397
01:34:31,800 --> 01:34:32,560
[SPEAKER_02] ako je zazovemo,

1398
01:34:32,560 --> 01:34:34,000
[SPEAKER_02] to onda ima smisla,

1399
01:34:34,000 --> 01:34:36,760
[SPEAKER_02] jer ona predstavlja njezinu prisutnost.

1400
01:34:36,760 --> 01:34:38,760
[SPEAKER_00] Kronica je blagoslovljena sama po sebi,

1401
01:34:38,760 --> 01:34:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] uz sav respekt,

1402
01:34:39,739 --> 01:34:41,680
[SPEAKER_00] ne igra puno

1403
01:34:41,680 --> 01:34:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] ako se mi prema njoj ne odnosimo,

1404
01:34:43,779 --> 01:34:45,779
[SPEAKER_00] prema onomu što ona simbolizira u stvari.

1405
01:34:45,779 --> 01:34:49,239
[SPEAKER_01] Potrebno je naša vjera naših srca.

1406
01:34:49,239 --> 01:34:50,340
[SPEAKER_01] Naša vjera, naravno,

1407
01:34:50,340 --> 01:34:51,079
[SPEAKER_02] uvijek ne može,

1408
01:34:51,079 --> 01:34:54,600
[SPEAKER_02] znači nije to sve tako matematički proračunato,

1409
01:34:54,600 --> 01:34:57,119
[SPEAKER_02] dakle, Bog uvijek može djelovati,

1410
01:34:57,119 --> 01:35:00,199
[SPEAKER_02] jer si ti jednom u vjeri stavio tu,

1411
01:35:00,279 --> 01:35:00,760
[SPEAKER_02] u vjernicu,

1412
01:35:00,760 --> 01:35:03,720
[SPEAKER_02] a onda si živio ovako i onako.

1413
01:35:03,720 --> 01:35:08,560
[SPEAKER_02] Tajan tvoj čin je ipak dotaknuo milosrednog oca

1414
01:35:08,560 --> 01:35:12,659
[SPEAKER_02] i dao mu prostor da on ima utjecaj na tvoj život,

1415
01:35:12,659 --> 01:35:13,420
[SPEAKER_02] da te spasi.

1416
01:35:13,420 --> 01:35:16,899
[SPEAKER_00] A zašto blagosljivljamo kuće stanove?

1417
01:35:16,899 --> 01:35:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je jednom godišnjim minimalno.

1418
01:35:18,920 --> 01:35:22,000
[SPEAKER_02] To su me pitali mnogi.

1419
01:35:22,000 --> 01:35:23,619
[SPEAKER_02] To mnogi pitu.

1420
01:35:23,619 --> 01:35:24,840
[SPEAKER_02] Neću ja više blagosljivljati.

1421
01:35:24,840 --> 01:35:26,039
[SPEAKER_02] Prošle godine ste blagoslovili,

1422
01:35:26,039 --> 01:35:27,340
[SPEAKER_02] šta ću sad blagosljivljati?

1423
01:35:27,340 --> 01:35:28,760
[SPEAKER_02] Toga bude.

1424
01:35:30,279 --> 01:35:31,180
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

1425
01:35:31,180 --> 01:35:33,539
[SPEAKER_02] blagosljivljaju se obitelji,

1426
01:35:33,539 --> 01:35:34,420
[SPEAKER_02] ljudi.

1427
01:35:34,420 --> 01:35:35,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1428
01:35:35,239 --> 01:35:36,119
[SPEAKER_02] Ali nije samo to,

1429
01:35:36,119 --> 01:35:37,500
[SPEAKER_02] blagosljivljaju se i stanovi.

1430
01:35:37,500 --> 01:35:39,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ali mi živimo u tim stanovima.

1431
01:35:39,420 --> 01:35:42,000
[SPEAKER_02] U tim stanovima se kroz godinu dana nešto događa.

1432
01:35:42,000 --> 01:35:43,699
[SPEAKER_02] Neko opsuje,

1433
01:35:43,699 --> 01:35:45,000
[SPEAKER_02] neko se posvađa,

1434
01:35:45,000 --> 01:35:46,119
[SPEAKER_02] neko se potuče,

1435
01:35:46,119 --> 01:35:48,420
[SPEAKER_02] neko ukrade novce,

1436
01:35:48,420 --> 01:35:49,420
[SPEAKER_02] mami, taj ti.

1437
01:35:49,420 --> 01:35:51,060
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, svajno se tu događa.

1438
01:35:51,619 --> 01:35:52,439
[SPEAKER_02] Neko slaže,

1439
01:35:52,439 --> 01:35:53,279
[SPEAKER_02] neko izvrijeđa,

1440
01:35:53,279 --> 01:35:54,159
[SPEAKER_02] neko proklinje.

1441
01:35:54,159 --> 01:35:54,720
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

1442
01:35:54,720 --> 01:35:57,140
[SPEAKER_02] to su razlozi.

1443
01:35:57,140 --> 01:35:58,619
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto treba ponovo?

1444
01:35:58,619 --> 01:36:02,020
[SPEAKER_02] To je kao jedno obnavljanje.

1445
01:36:02,020 --> 01:36:03,779
[SPEAKER_02] Zapravo, kad se ide tamo gledati šta je to,

1446
01:36:03,779 --> 01:36:05,600
[SPEAKER_02] to je obnavljanje saveza s Bogom.

1447
01:36:05,600 --> 01:36:06,380
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

1448
01:36:06,380 --> 01:36:09,239
[SPEAKER_02] obnavljanje svih onih situacija

1449
01:36:09,239 --> 01:36:12,159
[SPEAKER_02] gdje smo mi prekršili save s Bogom.

1450
01:36:12,159 --> 01:36:13,199
[SPEAKER_02] Mi ga vraćamo

1451
01:36:13,199 --> 01:36:15,500
[SPEAKER_02] i sve te situacije vraćamo

1452
01:36:15,500 --> 01:36:16,720
[SPEAKER_02] pod blagoslov Boži.

1453
01:36:16,720 --> 01:36:19,819
[SPEAKER_02] I molimo iscijeljenje

1454
01:36:19,819 --> 01:36:22,479
[SPEAKER_02] tih međusobnih nekih stvari

1455
01:36:22,479 --> 01:36:23,479
[SPEAKER_02] koje su se događale,

1456
01:36:23,479 --> 01:36:24,420
[SPEAKER_02] povrijeđenosti,

1457
01:36:24,420 --> 01:36:25,560
[SPEAKER_02] narošenih odnosa,

1458
01:36:25,560 --> 01:36:26,739
[SPEAKER_02] oprosta.

1459
01:36:26,739 --> 01:36:27,939
[SPEAKER_02] To je razlog.

1460
01:36:27,939 --> 01:36:31,100
[SPEAKER_02] Zapravo, gospodin

1461
01:36:31,100 --> 01:36:32,439
[SPEAKER_02] koga smo istjerali van,

1462
01:36:32,439 --> 01:36:34,300
[SPEAKER_02] možda s svojim životom

1463
01:36:34,300 --> 01:36:36,539
[SPEAKER_02] da ga opet uvedemo unutra.

1464
01:36:36,539 --> 01:36:38,199
[SPEAKER_01] Oprosti, ako se mogu,

1465
01:36:38,279 --> 01:36:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] da paće, da paće.

1466
01:36:39,420 --> 01:36:39,939
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo,

1467
01:36:39,939 --> 01:36:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] iskustvo kad idete

1468
01:36:41,880 --> 01:36:42,859
[SPEAKER_01] evangelizirati pa dođete

1469
01:36:42,859 --> 01:36:43,979
[SPEAKER_01] u neki drugo mjesto

1470
01:36:43,979 --> 01:36:45,560
[SPEAKER_01] i sad spavate negdje

1471
01:36:45,560 --> 01:36:48,119
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je turističko naselje

1472
01:36:48,119 --> 01:36:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] i vrlo često djeti

1473
01:36:51,579 --> 01:36:52,779
[SPEAKER_01] mogu biti netko drugi

1474
01:36:52,779 --> 01:36:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] spavat na tom krevetu.

1475
01:36:53,840 --> 01:36:55,479
[SPEAKER_01] I onda iskustvo pokazuje

1476
01:36:55,479 --> 01:36:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je dobro

1477
01:36:56,159 --> 01:36:57,939
[SPEAKER_01] kad dođeš u tu sobu

1478
01:36:57,939 --> 01:37:00,279
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek zamoliti gospodina blagoslovak,

1479
01:37:00,279 --> 01:37:01,319
[SPEAKER_01] imaš posjećenu vodu,

1480
01:37:01,319 --> 01:37:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] zamoliti da se opraste

1481
01:37:02,199 --> 01:37:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] svi grijesi koji su se tu dogodili.

1482
01:37:03,659 --> 01:37:05,359
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, iskustvo.

1483
01:37:05,359 --> 01:37:06,199
[SPEAKER_01] Oni koji tako rade,

1484
01:37:06,199 --> 01:37:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] i moje osobno,

1485
01:37:07,239 --> 01:37:08,239
[SPEAKER_01] ako nekad, ono,

1486
01:37:08,239 --> 01:37:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] nemaš dovoljno vremena,

1487
01:37:09,460 --> 01:37:11,079
[SPEAKER_01] onda zna biti burna noć.

1488
01:37:11,079 --> 01:37:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] Budu malo, ajmo reći,

1489
01:37:12,960 --> 01:37:13,520
[SPEAKER_01] ometanja,

1490
01:37:13,520 --> 01:37:14,520
[SPEAKER_01] ne moraš zaspati,

1491
01:37:14,520 --> 01:37:16,140
[SPEAKER_01] koje kakve napasti.

1492
01:37:16,140 --> 01:37:18,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad čovjek uđe u molite,

1493
01:37:18,140 --> 01:37:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] o baš jedan brat,

1494
01:37:19,300 --> 01:37:20,680
[SPEAKER_01] je isto tako,

1495
01:37:20,680 --> 01:37:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] kaže,

1496
01:37:21,199 --> 01:37:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] jedan svećenik je baš rekao,

1497
01:37:22,500 --> 01:37:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] kaže,

1498
01:37:23,020 --> 01:37:24,060
[SPEAKER_01] nikog ja nigdje ne dođem,

1499
01:37:24,060 --> 01:37:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] a ne spavam,

1500
01:37:25,000 --> 01:37:26,020
[SPEAKER_01] a da na vrh krevete,

1501
01:37:26,020 --> 01:37:26,840
[SPEAKER_01] i na dno krevete,

1502
01:37:26,840 --> 01:37:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] nastavim znak križa,

1503
01:37:28,420 --> 01:37:30,439
[SPEAKER_01] i blagoslov zaštite.

1504
01:37:30,439 --> 01:37:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

1505
01:37:31,380 --> 01:37:32,819
[SPEAKER_01] snaga vode,

1506
01:37:32,819 --> 01:37:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] ude,

1507
01:37:33,079 --> 01:37:33,520
[SPEAKER_01] soli,

1508
01:37:33,520 --> 01:37:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] ali snaga blagoslova našeg,

1509
01:37:35,300 --> 01:37:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] koje mi možemo,

1510
01:37:35,960 --> 01:37:36,899
[SPEAKER_01] bilo kao svećenici,

1511
01:37:36,899 --> 01:37:37,979
[SPEAKER_01] bilo kao lajci,

1512
01:37:37,979 --> 01:37:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] izreć,

1513
01:37:38,380 --> 01:37:40,260
[SPEAKER_01] jer sve to pismo nam o tome govori.

1514
01:37:40,260 --> 01:37:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže,

1515
01:37:40,460 --> 01:37:42,199
[SPEAKER_01] blagosiv dajte svoje neprijatelje.

1516
01:37:42,680 --> 01:37:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] Molite za one koji vas progojne.

1517
01:37:44,079 --> 01:37:46,020
[SPEAKER_01] Samim time što mi izgovaramo,

1518
01:37:46,020 --> 01:37:47,300
[SPEAKER_01] Boži blagoslov,

1519
01:37:47,300 --> 01:37:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] zazvavamo Božje ime,

1520
01:37:48,380 --> 01:37:49,359
[SPEAKER_01] Božju ljubav,

1521
01:37:49,359 --> 01:37:49,939
[SPEAKER_01] dobrotu,

1522
01:37:49,939 --> 01:37:52,439
[SPEAKER_01] mi već time poništavamo ono zlo,

1523
01:37:52,439 --> 01:37:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] koje dolazi,

1524
01:37:53,680 --> 01:37:55,079
[SPEAKER_01] možda protiv nas,

1525
01:37:55,079 --> 01:37:56,399
[SPEAKER_01] ili koje se na neki način,

1526
01:37:56,399 --> 01:37:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] ulovilo za nešto.

1527
01:37:58,960 --> 01:38:00,399
[SPEAKER_00] To sam u stvari htio pitati.

1528
01:38:00,399 --> 01:38:03,020
[SPEAKER_00] Mimo blagoslova obitelji,

1529
01:38:03,020 --> 01:38:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] koji obično se radiju oko Božića,

1530
01:38:04,920 --> 01:38:07,020
[SPEAKER_00] ti si niko spominjao,

1531
01:38:07,020 --> 01:38:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] taj duhovni boj za prostore,

1532
01:38:10,460 --> 01:38:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] ili slično,

1533
01:38:11,239 --> 01:38:11,939
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi je zanimalo,

1534
01:38:12,619 --> 01:38:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo, možda jedan primjer.

1535
01:38:13,880 --> 01:38:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] Patr Sebastian je spomenuo

1536
01:38:16,619 --> 01:38:18,520
[SPEAKER_01] kako kad se negdje nešto događa loše,

1537
01:38:18,520 --> 01:38:19,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer smo imali smenu situaciju

1538
01:38:19,760 --> 01:38:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je jedan samostan,

1539
01:38:21,800 --> 01:38:23,439
[SPEAKER_01] evo baš to je jedan specifičan primjer,

1540
01:38:23,439 --> 01:38:26,199
[SPEAKER_01] su imali jako veliki poteškoća

1541
01:38:26,199 --> 01:38:26,840
[SPEAKER_01] da ga obnove,

1542
01:38:26,840 --> 01:38:28,319
[SPEAKER_01] znači da ga obnove

1543
01:38:28,319 --> 01:38:30,819
[SPEAKER_01] i uvijek su imali nekakva čudna događanja,

1544
01:38:30,819 --> 01:38:31,600
[SPEAKER_01] ima reći unutar,

1545
01:38:31,600 --> 01:38:33,020
[SPEAKER_01] unutar samostana, duhovna.

1546
01:38:33,020 --> 01:38:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] A što je bilo,

1547
01:38:34,199 --> 01:38:35,819
[SPEAKER_01] taj samostan je bio duže vrijeme

1548
01:38:35,819 --> 01:38:37,100
[SPEAKER_01] u biti oduzet

1549
01:38:37,100 --> 01:38:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] i tamo su se događale svakakve stvari,

1550
01:38:39,779 --> 01:38:42,180
[SPEAKER_01] a kroz ratove i kroz vrijeme

1551
01:38:42,180 --> 01:38:44,319
[SPEAKER_01] bilo je zlostavljanje i ubojstava

1552
01:38:44,319 --> 01:38:44,979
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

1553
01:38:44,979 --> 01:38:48,899
[SPEAKER_01] I tada su ti svećenici tražili pomoć

1554
01:38:48,899 --> 01:38:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] i onda su došli ljudi

1555
01:38:50,300 --> 01:38:52,859
[SPEAKER_01] koji su na takav način

1556
01:38:52,859 --> 01:38:54,100
[SPEAKER_01] imali jedno iskustvo

1557
01:38:54,100 --> 01:38:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] i znali su

1558
01:38:54,739 --> 01:38:57,100
[SPEAKER_01] i nakon toga,

1559
01:38:57,100 --> 01:38:58,060
[SPEAKER_01] nakon tih molitvi,

1560
01:38:58,060 --> 01:39:00,220
[SPEAKER_01] nakon prolaska kroz pokajanje,

1561
01:39:00,220 --> 01:39:02,020
[SPEAKER_01] opraštanje, davanja zadovoljištine,

1562
01:39:02,020 --> 01:39:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] blagoslove prostora

1563
01:39:04,000 --> 01:39:06,020
[SPEAKER_01] i određene druge molitve

1564
01:39:06,020 --> 01:39:06,819
[SPEAKER_01] koje su tamo bile,

1565
01:39:06,819 --> 01:39:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] od jedan po se počelo stvar čistiti.

1566
01:39:09,000 --> 01:39:10,779
[SPEAKER_01] Oni godinama nisu mogli koraka napred,

1567
01:39:10,779 --> 01:39:11,819
[SPEAKER_01] nisu mogli iskoračiti,

1568
01:39:11,819 --> 01:39:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno koda je nešto blokiralo.

1569
01:39:14,039 --> 01:39:16,560
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga samostan se počeo obnavljati,

1570
01:39:16,560 --> 01:39:17,939
[SPEAKER_01] svi oni pritici koji su imali

1571
01:39:17,939 --> 01:39:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] od jedan po su nestali,

1572
01:39:19,500 --> 01:39:21,279
[SPEAKER_01] ono ljudi sad dolaze tamo,

1573
01:39:21,279 --> 01:39:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] jedna prekrasna atmosfera.

1574
01:39:23,380 --> 01:39:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] Zato želimo reći,

1575
01:39:24,500 --> 01:39:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] znači grijeh kad se dogodi

1576
01:39:26,340 --> 01:39:27,560
[SPEAKER_01] bilo na prostoru,

1577
01:39:27,560 --> 01:39:28,439
[SPEAKER_01] bilo u našem srcu,

1578
01:39:28,439 --> 01:39:30,319
[SPEAKER_01] potrebno ga ispovijediti i okajak,

1579
01:39:30,319 --> 01:39:31,479
[SPEAKER_01] ali dati zadovoljština.

1580
01:39:31,479 --> 01:39:33,880
[SPEAKER_01] Da Božja Milošt se opet nastani

1581
01:39:33,880 --> 01:39:35,779
[SPEAKER_01] na tom prostoru.

1582
01:39:35,779 --> 01:39:37,479
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako zvano

1583
01:39:37,479 --> 01:39:40,760
[SPEAKER_02] infestacijo ili zagađenje prostora.

1584
01:39:40,760 --> 01:39:42,800
[SPEAKER_02] Osim što zli djeluje na ljude,

1585
01:39:42,800 --> 01:39:44,260
[SPEAKER_02] on iskoristi i prostore

1586
01:39:44,260 --> 01:39:45,479
[SPEAKER_02] gdje ljudi griješe,

1587
01:39:45,479 --> 01:39:47,420
[SPEAKER_02] da bi nekako svoje...

1588
01:39:47,420 --> 01:39:48,939
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi značilo dati zadovoljštinu?

1589
01:39:48,939 --> 01:39:49,680
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon što smo,

1590
01:39:49,680 --> 01:39:50,979
[SPEAKER_00] isto gledam kroz ispovijed,

1591
01:39:51,460 --> 01:39:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] otiđeš, pokaješ se

1592
01:39:52,960 --> 01:39:54,500
[SPEAKER_00] i dobiš pokoru.

1593
01:39:54,500 --> 01:39:55,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jel pokora zadovoljština,

1594
01:39:55,720 --> 01:39:56,600
[SPEAKER_00] zadovoljština nešto

1595
01:39:56,600 --> 01:39:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] još nakon pokore?

1596
01:39:57,420 --> 01:40:00,619
[SPEAKER_02] Pokora to je zadovoljština za grijeh.

1597
01:40:00,619 --> 01:40:03,199
[SPEAKER_02] Ština može biti ozbiljna

1598
01:40:03,199 --> 01:40:04,039
[SPEAKER_02] i neozbiljna.

1599
01:40:04,960 --> 01:40:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ovisi u kakvim se situacijama događala.

1600
01:40:08,500 --> 01:40:10,260
[SPEAKER_01] I onda te jedno sa mno

1601
01:40:10,260 --> 01:40:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] može gospodina dahnut

1602
01:40:12,500 --> 01:40:14,260
[SPEAKER_01] kako treba dati zadovoljštinu.

1603
01:40:14,260 --> 01:40:15,600
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo možda je bila nekakva

1604
01:40:15,600 --> 01:40:18,220
[SPEAKER_01] financijska prevara

1605
01:40:18,220 --> 01:40:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] ili tako nešto

1606
01:40:19,079 --> 01:40:20,779
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je neko ostao dužan neke novce.

1607
01:40:20,779 --> 01:40:22,640
[SPEAKER_01] Onda zadovoljština može značiti

1608
01:40:22,640 --> 01:40:25,220
[SPEAKER_01] jedan dio nadoknade toga,

1609
01:40:25,220 --> 01:40:27,100
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo pokajanje.

1610
01:40:27,100 --> 01:40:27,619
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijem.

1611
01:40:28,420 --> 01:40:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijem.

1612
01:40:31,579 --> 01:40:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom sam čuo

1613
01:40:34,920 --> 01:40:37,100
[SPEAKER_00] dogledano filmu.

1614
01:40:37,100 --> 01:40:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali filmu koji su rekli

1615
01:40:38,619 --> 01:40:39,819
[SPEAKER_00] da je dosta realno

1616
01:40:39,819 --> 01:40:42,439
[SPEAKER_00] kada se tiče tih priča

1617
01:40:42,439 --> 01:40:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] o egzorcizmu.

1618
01:40:43,960 --> 01:40:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je bio obred

1619
01:40:45,619 --> 01:40:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] sa Anthony Hopkinsom.

1620
01:40:46,699 --> 01:40:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dosta nije ono bombasičan.

1621
01:40:52,539 --> 01:40:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] I dobre poanta na kraju.

1622
01:40:54,640 --> 01:40:55,760
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom da

1623
01:40:55,760 --> 01:40:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je bitan taj sakramentalni

1624
01:40:58,300 --> 01:40:59,100
[SPEAKER_00] život da

1625
01:40:59,100 --> 01:41:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] je

1626
01:41:01,420 --> 01:41:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] zli duh

1627
01:41:03,340 --> 01:41:06,060
[SPEAKER_00] kroz osobu koja se nalazila tamo

1628
01:41:06,060 --> 01:41:06,979
[SPEAKER_00] na egzorcizmu

1629
01:41:06,979 --> 01:41:09,439
[SPEAKER_00] zna on nabrajat

1630
01:41:09,439 --> 01:41:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] grijehe osobe koje nisu ispovjeđene.

1631
01:41:11,359 --> 01:41:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Je li to točno?

1632
01:41:11,960 --> 01:41:13,420
[SPEAKER_00] Može.

1633
01:41:13,420 --> 01:41:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] Je li on ima općenito

1634
01:41:14,500 --> 01:41:15,979
[SPEAKER_00] nekakva skrivena znanja koja?

1635
01:41:15,979 --> 01:41:17,859
[SPEAKER_02] Znači ovako

1636
01:41:17,859 --> 01:41:21,539
[SPEAKER_02] može imati

1637
01:41:21,539 --> 01:41:24,479
[SPEAKER_02] ali on ne čita misli.

1638
01:41:24,479 --> 01:41:26,020
[SPEAKER_02] To treba razlikovati.

1639
01:41:26,020 --> 01:41:27,779
[SPEAKER_02] Znači on ne čita misli

1640
01:41:27,779 --> 01:41:28,579
[SPEAKER_02] nego on promatra

1641
01:41:28,579 --> 01:41:29,180
[SPEAKER_02] tvoj život

1642
01:41:29,180 --> 01:41:30,859
[SPEAKER_02] i on vidi koji su tvoji grijesi.

1643
01:41:30,859 --> 01:41:32,060
[SPEAKER_02] Razumiješ?

1644
01:41:32,479 --> 01:41:34,140
[SPEAKER_02] znači on ubire obrazac

1645
01:41:34,140 --> 01:41:34,899
[SPEAKER_02] ali ne može

1646
01:41:34,899 --> 01:41:36,000
[SPEAKER_02] unutra

1647
01:41:36,000 --> 01:41:37,199
[SPEAKER_02] on ne čita misli.

1648
01:41:37,199 --> 01:41:38,659
[SPEAKER_02] ali kad se ti ispovjediš

1649
01:41:38,659 --> 01:41:42,039
[SPEAKER_02] on sve se bruši.

1650
01:41:42,039 --> 01:41:43,659
[SPEAKER_02] nema ni povijesti

1651
01:41:43,659 --> 01:41:45,500
[SPEAKER_02] niti ničega.

1652
01:41:45,500 --> 01:41:47,960
[SPEAKER_02] znači on nema pristupa više tomu.

1653
01:41:47,960 --> 01:41:49,380
[SPEAKER_02] ali ovo je važno znači.

1654
01:41:49,380 --> 01:41:51,699
[SPEAKER_02] znači on ne može da se boja da on nama čita misli.

1655
01:41:51,699 --> 01:41:54,220
[SPEAKER_02] nego on je super inteligentan.

1656
01:41:54,220 --> 01:42:00,439
[SPEAKER_02] znači on vidi po nama kako se ponašamo, gdje gledamo, kako slušamo naše slabosti.

1657
01:42:00,520 --> 01:42:02,800
[SPEAKER_02] a i vidio je grijehe koji nisu ispovjeđeni, ja.

1658
01:42:02,800 --> 01:42:06,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ali u duhovnom svijetu se vidi i ta vatra koju nosimo.

1659
01:42:06,640 --> 01:42:07,739
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo svjetlo svijeta.

1660
01:42:07,739 --> 01:42:15,600
[SPEAKER_01] Grad koji, kako kaže Isus koji je na gori, da li je sol zaista slana koja treba zasoliti ovaj svijet, da li to je svjetlo svijetli.

1661
01:42:15,600 --> 01:42:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] I u duhovnom svijetu se to vidi.

1662
01:42:17,840 --> 01:42:23,479
[SPEAKER_01] I znači ako ja ne živim svoje kršćanstvo, ako ja ne živim svoj duboki odnos s Bogom, to se očituje.

1663
01:42:23,479 --> 01:42:29,239
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno ako netko ima jako zajedništvo s Bogom i neka zajednica ima jako zajedništvo zajedno oko gospodina,

1664
01:42:29,239 --> 01:42:31,479
[SPEAKER_01] ne prijatelj to vidi, on se ne može lako približiti.

1665
01:42:31,479 --> 01:42:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je kao neprobojna utvoda.

1666
01:42:33,739 --> 01:42:41,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako on vidi i prepozna u nama da mi ogovaramo, da mi imamo neke tajne skrivene grijehe koje mislimo da niko ne vidi,

1667
01:42:41,439 --> 01:42:46,479
[SPEAKER_01] ne želimo ih se riješiti, ne želimo, mi time otvaramo na neki način ne samo sebe.

1668
01:42:47,159 --> 01:42:52,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nego ako sam ja otac obitelji i potajno, ne znam, primjer, imam problem sa pornografijom,

1669
01:42:52,460 --> 01:42:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo često i djeca kasnije imaju problem.

1670
01:42:55,260 --> 01:43:01,319
[SPEAKER_01] Niko nije vidio da je otac gledao pornografiju, ali se na neki način kao da se nakalemilo za djecu.

1671
01:43:01,319 --> 01:43:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ili tako može biti, ne znam, u zajednici ili neki problem, pa se to začas osjeti.

1672
01:43:06,840 --> 01:43:09,979
[SPEAKER_00] Sme menuli smo anđele čuvare, to mi je bilo pitanje.

1673
01:43:10,720 --> 01:43:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] Jel imate neko posebno iskustvo sa, recimo, nekom od posebnih pobožnosti da je super dijelotvorna,

1674
01:43:17,579 --> 01:43:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] ciljem na krunicu, ok, mislim, krunica se često spominje, pa može, ako imate neko iskustvo s tim,

1675
01:43:23,699 --> 01:43:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] ili recimo, da mislio da za vrijeme egzorcizama, možda je to individualno,

1676
01:43:28,060 --> 01:43:33,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali da se često zazivaju po neki sveci, koji su ekstra uspješni ili ih,

1677
01:43:34,340 --> 01:43:38,439
[SPEAKER_00] ti se reći, ili ih djavo jako ne voli, prepostavim da sve ne voli, ali neki koji su

1678
01:43:38,439 --> 01:43:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] specifični za određena područja.

1679
01:43:41,039 --> 01:43:46,020
[SPEAKER_02] Specifični i njihova snaga je bila već prepoznatljiva na ovom svijetu,

1680
01:43:46,020 --> 01:43:52,560
[SPEAKER_02] znači mi baš po njihovom zagovoru tu snagu oni stavljaju nama na raspolaganje.

1681
01:43:52,560 --> 01:43:54,380
[SPEAKER_02] Znači ono u čemu su na svijetu već bili?

1682
01:43:54,380 --> 01:43:59,399
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, da, već im je Bog dao, on i sada nama na tim područjima pomažu,

1683
01:43:59,399 --> 01:44:01,920
[SPEAKER_02] ako ih zazovemo, ako tražimo pomoć.

1684
01:44:02,079 --> 01:44:02,579
[SPEAKER_02] A gospa?

1685
01:44:02,579 --> 01:44:05,319
[SPEAKER_01] Gospa je za sve, za sve.

1686
01:44:05,319 --> 01:44:10,020
[SPEAKER_01] A evo, i padre piva i mnogi sveci su znali reći da ako kad čovjek moli,

1687
01:44:10,020 --> 01:44:15,439
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, ružari, tri krunice, da je to puno jače nego jedan ezorcizan.

1688
01:44:15,439 --> 01:44:19,359
[SPEAKER_01] I bila je situacija, sjećam se sa Cvetim Levopoldom našim,

1689
01:44:19,359 --> 01:44:23,359
[SPEAKER_01] koji je jako volio gospu i doveli su mu jednu djevojku,

1690
01:44:23,359 --> 01:44:28,319
[SPEAKER_01] koja je bila baš, ajmo reći, teži slučaj i ezorcisti nisu ništa mogli napraviti,

1691
01:44:28,319 --> 01:44:31,359
[SPEAKER_01] doveli ga i k njemu, a on je nikako moletvodni oslobađanje,

1692
01:44:31,819 --> 01:44:36,920
[SPEAKER_01] on je samo rekao, draga majko, nemoj dopustiti da ovo tvoje djete pati.

1693
01:44:36,920 --> 01:44:40,439
[SPEAKER_01] I tada se dogodilo trenutno oslobođenje.

1694
01:44:40,439 --> 01:44:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da utjecanje našoj majici i svecima su takva snaga.

1695
01:44:47,119 --> 01:44:53,720
[SPEAKER_01] i anđeli, čuvari, naglasak je na čuvarima, oni kad s njima znamo, oni vam mogu pomoći u tolikim situacijama,

1696
01:44:53,720 --> 01:45:02,220
[SPEAKER_01] u među ljudskim odnosima, gdje zapne nekakva stvar ili, to evo, mnogi to imaju, koji su malo dugdje umoliti na iskustvo sa njima.

1697
01:45:02,220 --> 01:45:04,399
[SPEAKER_00] Bližimo se kraju, sad još jedno pitanje, izvlačim.

1698
01:45:06,039 --> 01:45:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] andđeli, čuvari su andđeli košto su demoni andđeli.

1699
01:45:09,460 --> 01:45:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ili moj andđeli, čuvari, meni je dovoljan protiv svih demona ili se on isto nekak rangiraju i poštuju hirarhiju?

1700
01:45:13,960 --> 01:45:16,060
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja moram zvati jačeg.

1701
01:45:16,060 --> 01:45:20,680
[SPEAKER_02] To ne bih znao reći, da postoji hirarhija.

1702
01:45:20,680 --> 01:45:22,020
[SPEAKER_02] Postoji, da.

1703
01:45:22,020 --> 01:45:24,260
[SPEAKER_02] Postoji i oni se drže toga.

1704
01:45:24,260 --> 01:45:31,260
[SPEAKER_02] I naravno da onda uvijek ima prednost jači po hirarhiji.

1705
01:45:31,260 --> 01:45:32,500
[SPEAKER_02] Ima veće sposobnost.

1706
01:45:32,500 --> 01:45:36,020
[SPEAKER_00] I nema tu puno borbe u principu, to je ono, misli, hirarhija odigra svoje.

1707
01:45:36,020 --> 01:45:40,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pa odigra, ali opet nije to matematika.

1708
01:45:40,960 --> 01:45:47,899
[SPEAKER_02] Bog nekad dopusti, kaže to, manđelu smiri se tamo, pusti da malo ovaj, da se će liči i tako dalje.

1709
01:45:47,899 --> 01:45:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

1710
01:45:49,159 --> 01:45:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] Baš je to sa anđelima, Bog je dao te korove, znači imaju postoji devet korova anđela.

1711
01:45:57,119 --> 01:46:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] Anđeli čuvari koji su tu baš dani nama da nas vode, da nas prate.

1712
01:46:02,300 --> 01:46:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] I naš zaista istinski pobožni život s gospodinom, opet se vraćamo.

1713
01:46:06,880 --> 01:46:12,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je naš motiv, zavisi gdje smo mi usmjeren.

1714
01:46:12,239 --> 01:46:21,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je moje usmjerenje upravo na to posjećenje, na ljubav, na Boga Otca, na život, zajedništva s Bogom, sa braćom i sestrama,

1715
01:46:21,819 --> 01:46:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] nikakav nije problem. Anđeli tada jako puno mogu nas izbaviti od bilo kakve nevolje.

1716
01:46:26,800 --> 01:46:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] Problem je ako ja idem onda svoje vode i ustrajem putem grijeha,

1717
01:46:30,039 --> 01:46:32,359
[SPEAKER_01] tada i anđeli gube snagu.

1718
01:46:32,359 --> 01:46:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] Oni nemaju na neki način, jer naša otpadnost od Boga i to što mi prljamo naše haljine,

1719
01:46:40,380 --> 01:46:46,979
[SPEAKER_01] one haljine koje se objale u ispovjedi, na neki način prljaju, jer oni su s nama povezani,

1720
01:46:46,979 --> 01:46:49,680
[SPEAKER_01] prljaju i njihove haljine i na neki način gubi snagu.

1721
01:46:49,680 --> 01:46:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] Sad zamislite i njih, nekad ono, nekad se sjetim kad znam da zgriješite,

1722
01:46:55,579 --> 01:46:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] mogu misliti, joj, kako je njemu sad?

1723
01:46:58,260 --> 01:47:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ja si zamislim, haljine mu smrde jako najpokvarenija pokvarena jaja.

1724
01:47:03,380 --> 01:47:06,100
[SPEAKER_01] A jadan je krivni dužan, a ja, ja.

1725
01:47:06,579 --> 01:47:12,020
[SPEAKER_01] I onda zamuliš ga za upraštenje i njega, jer trpi, ali koliko su vjerniji nam.

1726
01:47:12,020 --> 01:47:16,899
[SPEAKER_01] A to je sve zato što nas Bog toliko ljubi, što on nikad nas ne ostavlja same,

1727
01:47:16,899 --> 01:47:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] on jednostavno brine za nas, on je dobar tata.

1728
01:47:20,199 --> 01:47:24,100
[SPEAKER_01] On zna svaku našu blast na našoj glavi, puno bolje.

1729
01:47:24,100 --> 01:47:27,119
[SPEAKER_01] Sotona, on je tu, možemo reći, nebitan igrač.

1730
01:47:27,119 --> 01:47:30,979
[SPEAKER_01] Naš tata je najvažniji igrač i to je...

1731
01:47:30,979 --> 01:47:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono pitanje fokusa, da.

1732
01:47:32,159 --> 01:47:32,840
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je.

1733
01:47:32,840 --> 01:47:34,619
[SPEAKER_01] I to je ljepota, to je ljepota.

1734
01:47:34,619 --> 01:47:38,359
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ti znaš da si ti siguran, može se oko tebe rušiti ono što kaže planine,

1735
01:47:38,359 --> 01:47:42,239
[SPEAKER_01] može se događati, ne znam šta, ali ti znaš da si na dlanu očeve ruke.

1736
01:47:42,239 --> 01:47:46,199
[SPEAKER_01] Može ti doj sam osobno Lucifer i cijeli pakao stati ispred tebe,

1737
01:47:46,199 --> 01:47:48,439
[SPEAKER_01] a ti znaš da si na dlanu očeve ruke.

1738
01:47:48,439 --> 01:47:50,180
[SPEAKER_01] I šta on može?

1739
01:47:50,180 --> 01:47:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može ništa.

1740
01:47:51,260 --> 01:47:53,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa je hjerarhija.

1741
01:47:53,020 --> 01:47:54,039
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1742
01:47:54,039 --> 01:47:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] Je.

1743
01:47:54,920 --> 01:47:57,479
[SPEAKER_02] Je, hjerarhija je zeznota stvarno.

1744
01:47:58,300 --> 01:48:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] A toliko smo protiv te hjerarhije, čak si i crkva ispočitala kao,

1745
01:48:01,859 --> 01:48:04,279
[SPEAKER_00] je, šta ovi gore, znaju.

1746
01:48:04,279 --> 01:48:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] Pa imaš, imaš...

1747
01:48:05,920 --> 01:48:08,000
[SPEAKER_02] Hjerarhija čuva, baš čuva i...

1748
01:48:08,000 --> 01:48:08,659
[SPEAKER_02] Te da redi, jel?

1749
01:48:08,659 --> 01:48:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ima baš ova jedna knjiga, ima puno dobri knjiga koje se mogu naću

1750
01:48:13,880 --> 01:48:17,840
[SPEAKER_01] u našim katoličkim knjižarama na tim, po tom pitanju.

1751
01:48:18,100 --> 01:48:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] Bio jednom, mislim da se zove moj obsjednućan, italijan koji je...

1752
01:48:21,460 --> 01:48:24,520
[SPEAKER_01] Onda on kaže kako je on, recimo, kako je on morao proći borbe.

1753
01:48:24,520 --> 01:48:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] Vedno, super iskustva jer on je bio svjesna svega što se događa oko njega.

1754
01:48:28,300 --> 01:48:31,300
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže u tom trenutku, jednom trenutku kad je njega biskup,

1755
01:48:31,300 --> 01:48:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] koji kaže možda nije bio, ne znam kako tome je posjećan,

1756
01:48:34,840 --> 01:48:35,819
[SPEAKER_01] on ga je blagoslovio.

1757
01:48:35,819 --> 01:48:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] I on je vidio, rekao je, kolika je snaga blagoslova biskup.

1758
01:48:40,199 --> 01:48:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] I on je rekao, kaže, tada je doživio jako veliko lakšanje.

1759
01:48:44,279 --> 01:48:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] I zato je ta hjerarhija, Bog je dao svoje hjerarhiju

1760
01:48:48,300 --> 01:48:52,060
[SPEAKER_01] i zato jesu biskupi tu i zato mi njima trebamo biti poslušni.

1761
01:48:52,060 --> 01:48:53,659
[SPEAKER_01] I to je jedna onda ljepota.

1762
01:48:53,659 --> 01:48:58,359
[SPEAKER_01] Crkva je red, crkva je zajedništvo, crkva je Božja snaga.

1763
01:48:58,359 --> 01:49:03,180
[SPEAKER_00] Za kraj pitanje, spomenuli ste knjige,

1764
01:49:03,180 --> 01:49:06,180
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo sad tu načeli temu duhovnog boja i puno toga.

1765
01:49:06,180 --> 01:49:09,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ima neka knjiga, bar jedna da bi preporučili

1766
01:49:09,100 --> 01:49:12,279
[SPEAKER_00] da se ljudi mogu izuze u ovog podcasta, osim Biblije.

1767
01:49:13,279 --> 01:49:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] I katekizma.

1768
01:49:14,920 --> 01:49:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] I katekizma.

1769
01:49:16,039 --> 01:49:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi mogli pročitati više nešto što je ono,

1770
01:49:20,300 --> 01:49:24,100
[SPEAKER_00] da vi znate da je dobro, pitko čak možda.

1771
01:49:24,100 --> 01:49:26,680
[SPEAKER_02] Ima, ima knjiga ako koji ćeš.

1772
01:49:26,680 --> 01:49:30,100
[SPEAKER_02] Jedna, već je poslije niko.

1773
01:49:30,100 --> 01:49:31,960
[SPEAKER_02] Meni jedna knjiga koju sam u zadnjih,

1774
01:49:31,960 --> 01:49:34,960
[SPEAKER_02] prije možda 5-6 godina pročitao

1775
01:49:34,960 --> 01:49:38,300
[SPEAKER_02] koji koristio je od jednog isovca,

1776
01:49:38,300 --> 01:49:40,380
[SPEAKER_02] Dari Ku, a zove se duhovnost.

1777
01:49:40,380 --> 01:49:43,939
[SPEAKER_02] I onda ima jedan dio koji govori o duhovnoj borbi.

1778
01:49:43,939 --> 01:49:46,979
[SPEAKER_02] Koja je sasvim jedna drugačija perspektiva

1779
