1788
01:50:12,199 --> 01:50:15,340
[SPEAKER_02] Zato kad mi molimo, mi se ne tučemo,

1789
01:50:15,340 --> 01:50:17,520
[SPEAKER_02] ali mi kad se molimo, se borimo.

1790
01:50:17,520 --> 01:50:17,899
[SPEAKER_02] Jasno.

1791
01:50:17,899 --> 01:50:21,460
