1792
01:50:21,460 --> 01:50:25,220
[SPEAKER_02] ono koda neprijatelja prebije šakama i nogama.

1793
01:50:25,220 --> 01:50:27,579
[SPEAKER_02] A on kaže, ovo su alati

1794
